1
00:00:08,960 --> 00:00:09,519
Recently,

2
00:00:09,640 --> 00:00:12,439
two violent kidnapping and rape cases occurred in our city.

3
00:00:12,960 --> 00:00:14,000
Both female victims

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:16,039
were brutally abused by the perpetrator.

5
00:00:16,239 --> 00:00:17,800
We urge all citizens

6
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:20,120
to stay safe when going out at night.

7
00:00:28,079 --> 00:00:29,120
Driver!

8
00:00:31,120 --> 00:00:31,800
Driver!

9
00:00:40,880 --> 00:00:41,479
Open the door!

10
00:01:06,079 --> 00:01:06,879
Run!

11
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:09,120
Let's see where you can run.

12
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:13,439
Didn't you say

13
00:01:13,879 --> 00:01:15,239
you'd give me anything?

14
00:01:15,359 --> 00:01:15,879
Come on.

15
00:01:16,239 --> 00:01:17,280
Look at the camera and say it.

16
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:20,000
Let me see that slutty look of yours.

17
00:01:22,359 --> 00:01:23,159
Relax.

18
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:26,040
I'll be gentle.

19
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:27,680
Good girl.

20
00:01:27,959 --> 00:01:28,760
It won't hurt.

21
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,439
The victim, Meng Xiaoyi,

22
00:02:12,599 --> 00:02:14,000
a sales manager at a real estate company.

23
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:17,199
Last night, she got drunk entertaining clients at a KTV

24
00:02:17,479 --> 00:02:19,199
and left in a taxi in the early morning.

25
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,400
After being knocked out by the driver,

26
00:02:20,479 --> 00:02:22,719
she was taken to a place resembling an indoor pool.

27
00:02:23,039 --> 00:02:24,520
The crime scene has yet to be located.

28
00:02:24,759 --> 00:02:27,360
Meng Xiaoyi was brutally abused and sexually assaulted.

29
00:02:27,479 --> 00:02:28,639
When she woke up again,

30
00:02:28,639 --> 00:02:30,719
she'd been dumped in a field on the outskirts of town.

31
00:02:30,919 --> 00:02:32,479
A taxi again.

32
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:36,000
The two rape cases at the precinct also involved taxis.

33
00:02:36,639 --> 00:02:37,960
Could it be the same person?

34
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:39,719
Here's the plan, Lao Wang.

35
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:42,080
After the meeting, have the tech division

36
00:02:42,199 --> 00:02:43,439
run video analysis

37
00:02:43,439 --> 00:02:44,560
and trace the vehicle's route.

38
00:02:45,199 --> 00:02:45,759
Got it.

39
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:48,520
Where's Li Kaiyang?

40
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:16,319
The victim, Meng Xiaoyi, was entertaining clients

41
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:17,800
and got drunk,

42
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,759
which is why she left early.

43
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:24,360
This means she just picked a random cab.

44
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:29,360
This KTV's entrance doesn't face the main road,

45
00:03:30,479 --> 00:03:31,919
and there's no surveillance footage.

46
00:03:33,759 --> 00:03:36,479
The killer must have scouted the location in advance.

47
00:03:47,319 --> 00:03:48,000
Captain Zhao.

48
00:03:49,759 --> 00:03:51,000
How's the victim doing?

49
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,039
She's out of danger now.

50
00:03:52,319 --> 00:03:53,960
Fang Ping, head over to the precinct now.

51
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,919
Bring back the files on the two recent rape cases.

52
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:56,879
Yes, sir.

53
00:03:58,479 --> 00:04:00,199
The victim recalled the suspect's license plate.

54
00:04:00,199 --> 00:04:01,000
The last digit

55
00:04:06,319 --> 00:04:06,759
is 9.

56
00:04:08,439 --> 00:04:09,199
Excellent.

57
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:11,800
Shunzi.

58
00:04:11,879 --> 00:04:12,280
Here.

59
00:04:12,439 --> 00:04:13,719
I'll leave the tech department to you.

60
00:04:13,879 --> 00:04:14,439
Got it.

61
00:04:15,759 --> 00:04:16,519
Do you think

62
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:18,959
this case is linked to the precinct's cases?

63
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:21,360
A character was carved near the victim's navel,

64
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,240
and the suspect was wearing red gloves.

65
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,240
Chief Xing.

66
00:04:40,959 --> 00:04:42,319
The carving on the victim's abdomen,

67
00:04:42,759 --> 00:04:43,600
do you still remember it?

68
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,000
How could I forget?

69
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,240
It's been exactly 22 years.

70
00:05:12,399 --> 00:05:13,639
I can't believe he's back.

71
00:05:14,199 --> 00:05:14,720
Here.

72
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:15,519
Turn the character upside down.

73
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:16,160
It's...

74
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,319
㑤

75
00:05:23,759 --> 00:05:24,519
I remember now.

76
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:27,519
The 5.31 Major Kidnapping and Murder Case from 22 years ago.

77
00:05:27,759 --> 00:05:29,759
A "㑤" was also carved on the victim.

78
00:05:31,519 --> 00:05:32,800
That's just too strange.

79
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:34,519
Could it be...

80
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,879
Did someone really slip through the net in the 5.31 case?

81
00:05:42,959 --> 00:05:43,480
Li Kaiyang.

82
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:44,360
Li Kaiyang.

83
00:05:46,839 --> 00:05:47,519
Chief Xing.

84
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,920
"㑤" is a rare character.

85
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:52,079
For it to appear again in the exact same way,

86
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,920
I believe it's no coincidence.

87
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,439
22 years ago, you said

88
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:58,519
Red Gloves slipped through the net,

89
00:05:59,160 --> 00:06:00,439
and he was the one who carved the character.

90
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,879
Director Jiang and I investigated for years,

91
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:05,160
right up until he retired,

92
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,600
but we never found any valuable clues.

93
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:07,680
I know.

94
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:10,079
But not finding him doesn't mean he doesn't exist.

95
00:06:10,839 --> 00:06:11,800
I firmly believe Red Gloves

96
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,360
is definitely still watching us from the dark.

97
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:18,240
I know this has been weighing on you.

98
00:06:19,079 --> 00:06:20,560
You've always wanted to reopen this case.

99
00:06:21,199 --> 00:06:21,839
But

100
00:06:22,279 --> 00:06:23,600
relying solely on this single character now

101
00:06:23,839 --> 00:06:25,560
to conclude it's related to the old case

102
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,199
is still a bit of a stretch.

103
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,600
I need direct evidence.

104
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,240
It might be a copycat.

105
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:32,879
Otherwise, why would he vanish for 22 years

106
00:06:32,879 --> 00:06:33,720
only to resurface now?

107
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:35,079
It doesn't make sense.

108
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:37,040
But 22 years ago,

109
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,959
the details of the 5.31 case

110
00:06:39,199 --> 00:06:41,000
were never disclosed to the public.

111
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,040
Furthermore,

112
00:06:43,839 --> 00:06:45,079
the location of the carving

113
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,519
is exactly the same.

114
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:47,959
How do you explain that?

115
00:06:50,639 --> 00:06:52,759
There have been three consecutive cases recently.

116
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,759
They've caused severe public outrage.

117
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,240
We need to solve them as fast as possible.

118
00:06:58,959 --> 00:06:59,600
Li Kaiyang,

119
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:02,839
if you think this case is tied to Red Gloves,

120
00:07:03,519 --> 00:07:04,519
I want you to personally

121
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,120
put the evidence right in front of me.

122
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,079
Understood.

123
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:21,680
Hello, Captain Li.

124
00:07:21,879 --> 00:07:23,959
We found the suspect taxi, Jiang VN3869.

125
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:26,160
It's heading downtown from Tingjiang, Pingjiang District.

126
00:07:26,399 --> 00:07:27,399
Captain Zhao has already taken a team there.

127
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:28,680
Okay, got it.

128
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:29,720
I'll go intercept it now.

129
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,000
Captain Li,

130
00:07:31,399 --> 00:07:32,240
is there a new case?

131
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:35,160
Suspect taxi, Jiang VN3869.

132
00:07:35,319 --> 00:07:35,879
Keep an eye out for it.

133
00:07:35,879 --> 00:07:36,480
Okay.

134
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:47,680
Is that the car?

135
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,399
That's the one.

136
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:51,600
Hold on tight.

137
00:07:55,759 --> 00:07:56,680
Should we wait for backup?

138
00:07:57,279 --> 00:07:58,000
There's no time.

139
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:04,000
Police! Pull over!

140
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,639
Pull over! Stop the car!

141
00:08:14,279 --> 00:08:15,360
Fang Ping, check the vehicle.

142
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:15,920
Okay.

143
00:08:54,919 --> 00:08:56,919
Well, well. Quite a few accomplices.

144
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,240
Stay right there!

145
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:02,360
Police!

146
00:09:06,879 --> 00:09:07,799
Impersonating a cop now, are you?

147
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:49,759
Don't move! Don't move!

148
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,000
Put your hands up!

149
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:51,759
Behave yourself!

150
00:09:52,519 --> 00:09:54,320
I'm talking to you. Hands up!

151
00:09:57,759 --> 00:09:58,600
It's a misunderstanding!

152
00:09:58,960 --> 00:09:59,759
A huge misunderstanding!

153
00:09:59,759 --> 00:10:00,759
I'm a cop too.

154
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:01,480
Shut up!

155
00:10:02,159 --> 00:10:03,159
Did I say you could talk?

156
00:10:03,759 --> 00:10:04,440
You okay?

157
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:06,840
Why'd you act alone?

158
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:07,840
That's so dangerous!

159
00:10:12,919 --> 00:10:13,840
The handcuffs are his.

160
00:10:15,039 --> 00:10:16,480
You've got some nerve, kid.

161
00:10:16,879 --> 00:10:18,120
You even used his cuffs.

162
00:10:18,399 --> 00:10:20,000
No, it really is a misunderstanding.

163
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,519
I'm from Fu'an Police Station.

164
00:10:21,679 --> 00:10:22,559
Where's your ID?

165
00:10:23,039 --> 00:10:24,159
My ID's on me.

166
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:25,080
If you don't believe me, check.

167
00:10:27,759 --> 00:10:28,600
There's no ID here.

168
00:10:29,159 --> 00:10:29,799
No, wait.

169
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,759
It must've dropped during the fight.

170
00:10:32,039 --> 00:10:32,879
Search the area.

171
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,279
Uncuff him too.

172
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:38,639
He's not the suspect.

173
00:10:38,639 --> 00:10:39,200
Behave!

174
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:41,159
Ouch, easy, officer!

175
00:10:41,159 --> 00:10:41,840
Got him!

176
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,960
Uncuff me! Uncuff me!

177
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:45,200
The suspect taxi driver, Lin Xiaohu.

178
00:10:45,679 --> 00:10:46,320
Good work.

179
00:10:47,039 --> 00:10:47,840
Easy.

180
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:50,279
Captain Zhao, we found it.

181
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:56,679
Jiang Han.

182
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,080
What the hell is going on?

183
00:10:59,759 --> 00:11:00,639
You're Captain Zhao, right?

184
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:02,559
This really is a misunderstanding.

185
00:11:03,039 --> 00:11:05,120
Lin Xiaohu is a suspect in a theft case in our jurisdiction.

186
00:11:05,559 --> 00:11:06,600
I had impounded his car.

187
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,720
Then this guy cut me off.

188
00:11:07,879 --> 00:11:08,759
And then he ran.

189
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:10,759
I didn't do anything!

190
00:11:10,919 --> 00:11:12,440
Right, you didn't do anything?

191
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:13,320
Then why'd you run?

192
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,279
Hey, hey, hey!

193
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:17,000
He forced my car to stop.

194
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,039
And you two got into a fight.

195
00:11:18,039 --> 00:11:19,360
I was scared, of course I ran!

196
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,320
Enough with the nonsense.

197
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,159
Take him away.

198
00:11:22,799 --> 00:11:23,399
Let's go.

199
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,120
Nice moves.

200
00:11:30,559 --> 00:11:31,559
You're something else yourself.

201
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,559
You didn't cuff the suspect.

202
00:11:33,639 --> 00:11:34,759
Instead you cuffed one of our own.

203
00:11:34,919 --> 00:11:36,080
Not bad, kid.

204
00:11:36,399 --> 00:11:37,120
Right off the bat,

205
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:39,559
you beat up The Ultimate Brain of the Fengdu PD.

206
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:41,639
What?

207
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:43,840
You really made a huge mess this time.

208
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:46,480
How does it feel?

209
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:47,960
The taste of getting taken down,

210
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:48,759
not too great, huh?

211
00:11:50,279 --> 00:11:53,039
Don't tell me he's Fengdu's Superbrain Detective,

212
00:11:53,039 --> 00:11:54,960
The Ultimate Brain, Li Kaiyang?

213
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,159
Oh no.

214
00:11:57,679 --> 00:11:58,320
Bro.

215
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:01,159
I didn't know you were one of us.

216
00:12:01,279 --> 00:12:02,360
I hit you too hard.

217
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,080
Captain Zhao.

218
00:12:04,399 --> 00:12:06,600
Lin Xiaohu is just a theft suspect.

219
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:08,240
There's no need for such a big fuss, right?

220
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:11,759
You, you nearly caused a massive disaster.

221
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:15,919
Wrap it up.

222
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:32,159
Bro,

223
00:12:32,879 --> 00:12:34,519
I hit you pretty hard earlier, huh?

224
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:36,600
You were the one coming at me full force.

225
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:39,480
If I'd known you were the famous Captain Li,

226
00:12:39,799 --> 00:12:41,639
I wouldn't have dared lay a finger on you.

227
00:12:41,639 --> 00:12:42,759
But you did, didn't you?

228
00:12:44,919 --> 00:12:46,480
That's why I'm here to apologize.

229
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:47,720
You've gotta forgive me.

230
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:49,200
Otherwise I won't be able to eat or sleep.

231
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,200
I really didn't mean it.

232
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:50,919
Let go.

233
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:52,639
Forgive me first.

234
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:54,519
It was just a little misunderstanding.

235
00:12:54,639 --> 00:12:55,519
There's nothing to forgive.

236
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:56,600
Let go.

237
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:59,559
Bro, I won't lie to you.

238
00:12:59,799 --> 00:13:01,320
I'm about to transfer to the Criminal Investigation Unit too.

239
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:02,879
We might end up being colleagues.

240
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:07,559
The Criminal Investigation Unit doesn't need reckless brutes.

241
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:11,440
Hey, that's a one-sided view.

242
00:13:12,559 --> 00:13:14,639
Didn't you just say it was a misunderstanding?

243
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,480
Why'd you have to hit so hard?

244
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,399
But don't underestimate me.

245
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:25,039
I will definitely become an excellent detective.

246
00:13:25,159 --> 00:13:26,159
I'll show you what I'm made of.

247
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:27,279
Just you wait.

248
00:13:34,519 --> 00:13:35,679
How's the interrogation with Lin Xiaohu going?

249
00:13:37,799 --> 00:13:39,039
Didn't I tell you to go home and rest?

250
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:42,120
Just a few punches. I'm fine.

251
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:45,919
That punk hits pretty hard.

252
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,639
But you know what,

253
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,320
our Major Crimes Unit

254
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:52,440
really could use a fighter like him.

255
00:13:52,879 --> 00:13:54,200
What's that supposed to mean?

256
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,879
You think I didn't get beat up enough?

257
00:13:57,639 --> 00:13:58,320
Look at you.

258
00:13:58,879 --> 00:13:59,840
You just said you were fine.

259
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:03,279
Lin Xiaohu didn't even have the time to commit the crime.

260
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:05,799
Red Gloves just cloned his license plate.

261
00:14:06,759 --> 00:14:08,360
Red Gloves' methods are brutal.

262
00:14:08,679 --> 00:14:09,759
He leaves no traces at the scene.

263
00:14:10,159 --> 00:14:12,559
Using cloned plates is a basic skill for him.

264
00:14:14,679 --> 00:14:16,480
If you'd said so earlier, we wouldn't have wasted our time.

265
00:14:16,879 --> 00:14:18,360
Every possibility needs to be verified.

266
00:14:18,639 --> 00:14:20,440
Besides, even false leads can hide clues.

267
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,120
At least now we know

268
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:24,200
the suspect is using a license plate cloned from Lin Xiaohu's.

269
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:26,600
We can comb through the surveillance footage using that plate.

270
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:28,200
We may very well find useful clues.

271
00:14:29,039 --> 00:14:30,279
So it wasn't a wasted effort after all.

272
00:14:30,759 --> 00:14:32,080
This Lin Xiaohu is a gambling addict.

273
00:14:32,279 --> 00:14:33,080
From him,

274
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:35,120
we unexpectedly uncovered an underground gambling den.

275
00:14:35,679 --> 00:14:36,799
Team Two's got their work cut out for them tonight.

276
00:14:54,879 --> 00:14:56,399
I want to hear you bark like a dog.

277
00:14:58,440 --> 00:14:59,399
You can bark, can't you?

278
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:04,960
I'll bark, I'll bark.

279
00:15:05,159 --> 00:15:06,879
I'll bark, I'll bark.

280
00:15:08,399 --> 00:15:09,200
Bark again.
